items.badge_description: Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 50 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 11!
One cannot live on dank hops alone. Tone down the bitterness and enjoy some smooth flavor. That's 15 different beers with an IBU of 20 or below. Try 5 more for Level 4!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 25 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 6!

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 200 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 41!
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren’t you?. That’s 85 different Lagers! Try 5 more for Level 18!
